Subject: [PATCH] lighten the cpu load.

GetAsyncKeyState returns too frequently. Sleeping it should help. Lemme know if you guys have any issues with it, I only tested it briefly.
---
 gw2dps/gw2dps.cpp | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/gw2dps/gw2dps.cpp b/gw2dps/gw2dps.cpp
index 0a5301d..dd9079c 100644
--- a/gw2dps/gw2dps.cpp
+++ b/gw2dps/gw2dps.cpp
@@ -1623,7 +1623,7 @@ void GW2LIB::gw2lib_main()
 
 	// wait for exit hotkey
 	while (GetAsyncKeyState(VK_F12) >= 0)
-		;
+		Sleep(1);
 
 	close_config();
 
